channel.title: Hacking psp? Trying to find 4.01 M33-2 Apps
channel.description:
Has anybody hacked there psp? I recently turned my psp slim battery into a pandora, and then back. Yes, it is possible if you cut it in the correct spot.
My main question, does anybody know of some good applications or things for the '4.01 M33-2 firmware'?
